data.title: Adrianne Curry & Chris Knight in Counseling
data.meta_description: America's Next Top Model winner Adrianne Curry tells OK! that she and her hubby of one year, Brady Bunch alum Christopher Knight, are so committed to making
data.text:
America's Next Top Model winner tells OK! that she and her hubby of one year, Brady Bunch alum , are so committed to making their high-profile relationship work that they have opted to seek professional help.

OK! caught up with the model/reality star as she hosted the launch of the elite, new Von Dutch Watches Collection at the Tourneau store in Midtown Manhattan, where she revealed that she and Chris “are in counseling right now and doing a lot of hard work.”
